        <div class="view-offer">
            <p class="text-offer">Looking for the perfect gift for that special someone? Look no further than our gift cards! With our easy-to-use website, you can purchase gift cards in any amount, and send them instantly to your loved ones. Whether it's for a birthday, anniversary, or just to say "thank you," our gift cards are the perfect way to show you care. Plus, with no expiration date and the ability to use them on anything in our store, our gift cards are a gift that keeps on giving. So why wait? Purchase your gift card today and give the gift of choice and convenience!</p>
            <div class="sts-giftcard">
                <img src="/img/offer-card.jpg" alt="">
                <form action="">
